title: Burn Notice Graphic Novels
description:
This torrent contains 3 full length graphic novels from the show's USA Network web site and prior torrents combined. Unfortunately, the old torrents stopped half way through the 3rd volume, so I created those parts myself.  I'm not sure why the 3rd volume wasn't completed.  Maybe the source got burned?

Source http://newday.usanetwork.com/#library?1-12
